===Etymology===
From {{etyl|enm|en}} {{term|poudre||lang=enm}}, {{term|pouldre||lang=enm}}, {{etyl|fro|en}} {{term|poudre||lang=fro}}, {{term|poldre||lang=fro}}, {{term|puldre||lang=fro}}, {{etyl|la|en}} {{term|pulvis||lang=la|dust, powder}}. compare [[pollen]] fine flour, mill dust, E. pollen. Compare [[polverine]], [[pulverize]].

