===Verb===
{{en-verb}}

# {{context|transitive|lang=en}} To reduce to fine particles; to [[pound]], [[grind]], or [[rub]] into a powder.
# {{context|transitive|lang=en}} To sprinkle with powder, or as with powder.
#: ''to '''powder''' the hair''
#* {{rfdate}} [[w:John Milton|John Milton]]:
#*: A circling zone thou seest / '''Powdered''' with stars.
# {{context|intransitive|lang=en}} To be reduced to powder; to become like powder.
#: ''Some salts '''powder''' easily.''
# {{context|intransitive|lang=en}} To use powder on the hair or skin.
#: ''She paints and '''powders'''.''
# {{context|transitive|lang=en}} To [[sprinkle]] with [[salt]]; to [[corn]], as [[meat]].

